arts.ttl: AEK Larnaca vs Aberdeen predictions: Bajic to inspire hosts
arts.sum: AEK Larnaca have made the perfect start in the UEFA Conference League with two wins and the Cypriot side can take care of Aberdeen, with Enda McElhinney expecting Riad Bajic to continue his scoring streak in Europe.
